               <msContents>
                  <summary>Maṣḥafa geṣṣawe, Volume 1 of 3</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>Maṣḥafa geṣṣawe</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ግጽው። ዘወጽአ፡ በእንተ፡ ክብሮሙ፡ ወበዓላቲሆሙ፡ ለጻድቃን፡ ወለሰማዕት። በእንተ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ነቢያት፡ ወሐዋርያት።</incipit>
                     <note>Volume 1 of 3 arranged for the months of the year and major feasts: Maskaram, fol. 1r-48v; Ṭeqemt, fol. 48v-73v; Ḫedār, fol. 73v-114r; Tāḫśāś, fol. 114r-137v; Ṭerr, fol. 137v-173r; Yakkātit, fol. 173r-197v; Maggābit, fol. 197v-206r; Miyāzyā, fol. 206r-209v; Genbot, fol. 210r-213v; Fast of Lent, fol. 213v-224v. Continued in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML1166">Vol. 2 = EMML 1166</ref> and <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML1167">Vol. 3 = EMML 1167</ref>
                        
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="Codex">
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>
                           <material key="parchment"/>
                        </support>
                        <extent>
                           <measure unit="leaf">227</measure>
                           <dimensions type="outer" unit="mm">
                              <height>340</height>
                              <width>260</width>
                              <depth/>
                           </dimensions>
                        </extent>
                        <foliation>Stamped modern foliation in Arabic numerals</foliation>
                        <condition key="good"/>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc><layout columns="3" writtenLines="26"/></layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        Feśśeha Seyon (f. 3a) and Walda Giyorgis (f. 209b)
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc><decoNote xml:id="d1">Drawings of cross, fol. 226r-227r</decoNote></decoDesc>
                  <additions><list><item xml:id="e1">Copied by ፍሥሐ፡ ጽዮን, fol. 3r, and ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ, fol. 209v, for ጽጌ፡ ማርያም and his wife እሤተ፡ ማርያም. Colophon with date information, fol. 224v-225r; Prayer for civil and religious leaders, fol. 1r. The donation is noted also on the verso of the second for e guard leaf and on f. 209b. Stamp of Qannazmāc Segē, ff. 1a, 100b and 225a. Stamp of the Holy Trinity Cathedral, ff. 1a and 225a.
                     
                  </item></list></additions>
                  <bindingDesc><binding><decoNote xml:id="b1">Stamped leather over wood boards</decoNote></binding></bindingDesc>
                 
               </physDesc>
               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origDate when="1923"/>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>Note of ownership by ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ ሴም Walda Giyorgis Sēm on verso of the last rear guard leaf. Copied for (Qannazmac) ጽጌ፡ ማርያም Segē Māryām and his wife እሤተ፡ ማርያም  'Essēta Māryām (colophon 225r) who gave it to Makāna Śellāsē church.  In Holy Trinity Cathedral when filmed.</provenance>
               </history>
